OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will remain
OL,8,Fdry and mostly clear across all parts,
OL,9,Fperhaps a few shallow mist and fog
OL,10,Fpatches around dawn. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAny overnight mist and fog
OL,13,Fsoon clearing to leave a dry and sunny
OL,14,Fday. Very warm or hot with light east
OL,15,For northeast winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FStaying dry with plenty of sunshine.
OL,19,FVery warm or hot, becoming somewhat
OL,20,Fcooler on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
